Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.28,0:23:28.53,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}这一切——
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.53,0:23:32.71,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}现在都将改写
